4gpi-networkmanager (2.0.0) buster; urgency=medium

  * 4gpi-nm-helper:
    - Set APN settings from command line arguments
  * 4gpi-dbus-watcher:
    - Use python3-dbus instead of python3-pydbus
    - Get APN settings via dbus
  * debian/changelog: Fix format
  * debian/control: Update Depends
  * Update bash-completion
  * Update debhelper compatibility level to 12
  * Bump Standards-Version to 4.3.0

